<body>

    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="text-center">Privacy Policy for Book Borrowing System</h1>

        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>
            At <strong>Library World</strong>, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information.
            This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you borrow books from our system.
        </p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address.</li>
            <li><strong>Borrowing History:</strong> Information about the books you borrow, including titles, authors, and borrowing dates.</li>
            <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> If applicable, details of any penalties incurred or fees associated with late returns.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Book Borrowing Management:</strong> To process your book borrowing requests and maintain records of your borrowing history.</li>
            <li><strong>Communication:</strong> To send you notifications regarding your borrowed books, including reminders about due dates and penalties for late returns.</li>
            <li><strong>Improvements:</strong> To improve our services and user experience based on user feedback and usage data.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Data Protection</h2>
        <p>
            We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, and destruction.
            Access to your personal data is limited to authorized personnel who require it for the purposes outlined in this policy.
        </p>

        <h2>Late Return Penalties</h2>
        <p>
            We understand that circumstances may arise that prevent timely returns. However, to ensure fairness and accountability, we have established the following penalties for late returns:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Penalty Fee:</strong> A fee of [insert amount] will be charged for each day the book is overdue.</li>
            <li><strong>Maximum Penalty:</strong> The maximum penalty for any single book will not exceed [insert amount].</li>
            <li><strong>Loss of Borrowing Privileges:</strong> Repeated late returns may result in the suspension of your borrowing privileges for a period of [insert time period].</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>You have the right to access and update your personal information.</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your personal data, subject to any legal obligations to retain it.</li>
            <li>Withdraw your consent to the processing of your personal information at any time.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and we encourage you to review this policy periodically for any updates.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
            If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Email:</strong>Library World@example.com</li>
            <li><strong>Phone:</strong>+20111111111</li>
            <li><strong>Address:</strong>1st DownTown-Cairo-Egypt</li>
        </ul>
